com.google.devtools.build.lib.shell

Class Preconditions

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.devtools.build.lib.shell.Preconditions

  • public final class Preconditions
extends java.lang.Object
    Like Preconditions, but with overloads that avoid varargs-based array creation in checkArgument(boolean), checkState(boolean), and checkNotNull(T) for calls that list up to seven error message arguments when expression is true (or reference is non-null).

    Throughout this file, functions delegate to Preconditions methods of the same name for the purpose of readability and obvious semantics.
